description:
Minecraft Server. Today we get the MEGA Golden Ticket! from Iskall, and use it to farm up some gold to finish off the Ice Farm collection system. We check out the new non-stack item storage and mob system at the base. Then we head to shop town at spawn to get building a new business, Shade-E-E's.
